ComicInfo.Summary:
Deadpool finally remembers who he is! But now he's on a mission to figure out who the Deadpool imposters are... Before it's too late!
Deadpool tries to remember who he is. And there is success! Now it's time to find these Deadpool wannabes and see who's who. But what happens when T-Ray crashes the party? Oh no... this is another mistaken identity storyline...
